com.camerontec.catalys.server.component

Class ComponentCommandLineProcessor

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.camerontec.catalys.server.component.ComponentCommandLineProcessor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ICommandLineProcessor

    public class ComponentCommandLineProcessor
extends Object
implements ICommandLineProcessor
    Common Command Line Processor for all IComponents.

    This is a singleton - ie there is only one which handles the basic component commands for all IComponent objects.
